title: The Only Way Is Essex S16E13 Essexmas PDTV x264 TM mp4
description:
Christmas edition of the real-life soap. It will certainly be a Christmas to remember as three faces from the past return to the fold. Lauren Goodger is back in town and wastes no time in dishing out relationship advice to Danni, Mario Falcone drops in on Billie and Chloe to find out who has replaced him as Essex's bad boy, and Gemma Collins welcomes Lockie and Pete into her shop to catch up on the latest gossip. The gang also go on a festive break to a Scottish castle, but will there be romantic reunions and happy endings on the cards or will drama and devastation end up leaving the gang cold?

Huge thanks to TM for capping and sharing
